{"tid":631551,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"被造謠威脅並性侵鄭爽 導演陳嘉上要求當面對質","createTime":"2018-04-16T14:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T14:30:16.000Z","uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e9b2dd89870064d67312423bccd99c4c89e296e2","tid":631551,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/16/222933_30bd5d94992e050b1d048b5b9741385c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2F222933_30bd5d94992e050b1d048b5b9741385c.png&h=02cb56ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳嘉上微博<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/16/222933_23d88b06878c4d396892a6a1c0152446.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2F222933_23d88b06878c4d396892a6a1c0152446.png&h=8d1488f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳嘉上<br />\n<br />\n網易娛樂4月16日報導 陳嘉上發文中怒斥某&ldquo;尊貴的女星&rdquo;在與朋友聊天時造謠自己曾威脅鄭爽且性侵等。陳嘉上稱：&ldquo;我原對此等八卦胡編並不重視，但話出自一位尊貴的女星之口我不得不重視。&rdquo;他還表示，不知這位女士從何處得到這消息，他很願意與其對質。若不敢站出來就請立即停止這等不負責任的言論，否則將再公開追究。<br />\n<br />\n網友表示&ldquo;心疼陳嘉上導演&rdquo;，&ldquo;支持陳導維權&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.163.com/18/0416/14/DFH5PHEG00038FO9.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.163.com%2F18%2F0416%2F14%2FDFH5PHEG00038FO9.html&d=jl9%2FGclZ4d7fMGeX%2F4pQhf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=13d3d51b\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.163.com/18/0416/14/DFH5PHEG00038FO9.html</a>"}]}